component 0: [["When did Isaac Newton die?", "Isaac Newton died on March 20, 1727."]]

[["What were the key events and influences in Einstein's early education?", "Einstein's early education took place primarily in Munich and Zurich. He showed exceptional mathematical ability from a young age, but struggled with rote learning. His father, an electrician, nurtured his curiosity by encouraging him to ask questions about the world. In 1896, Einstein enrolled at the Swiss Federal Polytechnic (now ETH Zurich), where he studied mathematics and physics, laying the foundation for his future groundbreaking work in these fields."]]
